Form description
The theme AETHER delves into the often overlooked fifth element, representing that intrinsic force which brings out the true potential and unveils our authentic selves. While we commonly acknowledge air, water, fire, and earth, Aether symbolizes our core essence!

AETHER recognizes that the inner strength within each person varies. For some, it's a passion for creativity, for others, it's resilience in adversity or a deep sense of purpose driving them forward. This diversity highlights the richness of human experience and the different ways individuals find their AETHER.

Current Ticket Price : 
Single ticket: ₹499 
Group Tickets:
Group of 3: 10% OFF - 449/- per head. Total: 1347/- 
Group of 5: 20% OFF - 399/- per head. Total: 1995/-
NOTE:
 - A group ticket bought ONLINE has to be paid together as a single payment! Do not pay separately. Refer the same transaction ID in the individual forms.
 - Every member of the group must fill their own individual forms. YOU MUST DO THIS IN ORDER TO GET THE TICKET IN YOUR MAILS. Refer the single payment made for the Transaction ID asked.

A digital ticket will be sent to the provided email address

The theme AETHER delves into the often overlooked fifth element, representing that intrinsic force which brings out the true potential and unveils our authentic selves. While we commonly acknowledge air, water, fire, and earth, Aether symbolizes our core essence!

AETHER recognizes that the inner strength within each person varies. For some, it's a passion for creativity, for others, it's resilience in adversity or a deep sense of purpose driving them forward. This diversity highlights the richness of human experience and the different ways individuals find their AETHER.
